HWACOM SYSTEMS I said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 43.83% to NT$135,074,000 from NT$240,485,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            135,074          240,485    
YOY%             -43.83%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            829,428         1,143,648   
YOY%             -27.48% 
=================================================================
 